text: Piotr Kuczera (born 25 February 1995) is a Polish judoka. He is the 2016 European bronze medalist in the 90 kg division. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Polish male judoka Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:European Games competitors for Poland Category:Judoka at the 2019 European Games
